urls.description: I was honoured to be commissioned to design these beehives as a gift from Fortnum & Mason to HRH The Prince of Wales for his 70th birthday. The first drawing sho ws my initial concept of cladding standard hives, followed by 20 thumbnail sketches. These sketches were submitted to Prince Charles, and he chose three designs, which I then developed in more detail. The three detailed hive designs are shown in these pencil sketches, which were reproduced in an article about the project in the The Telegraph.
